First Department,

January, 1962

(January 4, 1962) The People of the State of New York v. Alfred Catino.

Motion for leave to appeal as a poor person granted to the extent and on the terms and conditions contained in the order of this court entered herein. Concur — Rabin, J. P., McNally, Stevens, Eager and Steuer, JJ.
